  <description><![CDATA[<p>The Hotel Hermitage is well-placed for exploring the UNESCO-listed hills of Cilento and Vallo di Diano National Park. Rocky peaks and green valleys surround the hotel, while a shuttle bus runs down to the nearby sandy beach. Or you could just spend your days at the hotel pools, which are overlooked by pine-green hills. Dinner is served in the restaurant, where you can try dishes using local ingredients like buffalo mozzarella and fresh seafood.</p>]]></description>
