  <facilityDescription><![CDATA[<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Restaurants &amp; Bars</strong></span></p>
<p>The hotel’s traditional restaurant serves Mediterranean cuisine and local produce from Cilento including buffalo mozzarella, fish and locally-grown vegetables.</p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Pool &amp; Beach</strong></span></p>
<p>A large pool (open mid May to September) is surrounded by the green vegetation of the Vallo di Diano National Park, meaning beautiful countryside views can be enjoyed while you relax on the sunlounger or go for a refreshing swim. There’s a second pool with a slide for children.</p>
<p>The beach can be accessed by the hotel’s free shuttle bus and is equipped with loungers, umbrellas, bar and pizzeria.</p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>General Facilities</strong></span></p>
<ul>
<li>Fitness room</li>
<li>Beauty centre</li>
<li>Football pitch</li>
<li>Tennis court</li>
</ul>]]></facilityDescription>
